.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, boat, trike, car, roller
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, poker, scrabble, domino
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
House: cape-cod, tower, farmhouse, futuristic, gothic-revival
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the trike
2. the person playing swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the person playing whist is the person drinking tea
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the car
5. the person driving the boat is the person drinking coffee
6. the farmhouse house is the owner of the bird
7. the person driving the roller is the tower house
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person playing scrabble is on the far left
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the tower house
12. the cape-cod house is the person drinking beer
13. the person playing poker is the futuristic house
14. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person driving the subway
15. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
